# Customer Churn Prediction Platform

An end-to-end Machine Learning Operations (MLOps) system designed to predict customer churn behavior and automate customer retention insights.

## 🚀 System Architecture
- **User Interface:** Streamlit Cloud Service
- **Model Engine:** Trained predictive classification model
- **Pipeline Automation:** Automated CI/CD execution via GitHub Actions

## 🛠️ Codebase Layout & Verification
- Clean Python project structure using an organized workspace layout.
- Fully compliant with **PEP 8 style rules** via verified local `flake8` and `black` formatter validation checks.